<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Oelschnitz</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Auskunft über die Gefangennahme des Albrecht Kodauer zu Gefrees.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_269" id="134v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_269_r1l8">Den von Ölſnıcʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_269_r1l9"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> wır <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . wıe daʒ Jr . den <expan>albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>kodaw<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒum gfreſſ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_269_r1l10">ʒu fenknuſſ bracht habt . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_269_r1l11">Jr vns bey dıſem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıben</expan> wellet Jn was <expan>leẅmu<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_269_r1l12"><expan>albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> kodawer <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſey vnd was Jr ſchuld ʒu Jm habt <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_269_r1l13">Jr Jn ʒu fenknuſſ habt <expan>brıng<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . als vıl eẅch des denn füklıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_269_r1l14">ſey . als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> . etc . das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . etc . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_269_r1l15"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_269" id="134v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Ölsnicz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> wir
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie daz ir den
                                                  <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>Kodaw<ex>er</ex></expan> zum Gfress zu
                                                fenknuss bracht habt. <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                                wir ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit
                                                fleiss, daz ir uns bey disem
                                                  <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreiben</expan> wellet, in was
                                                  <expan>lewmu<ex>n</ex>ts</expan>
<expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Kodawer
                                                  <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sey und was ir
                                                schuld zu im habt, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ir
                                                in zu fenknuss habt <expan>bring<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, als vil ewch des
                                                denn füklich sey, als wir
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> etc. Das
                                                  <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
